PackIt - WindowMenu
#fH2:The Window Menu
#Parent !Root

The Window menu is shown from the main window:

*Save*	This leads to the Save dialog to create the package. It will default to the recommended package name when first shown

*Export*	This leads to a sub menu that allows parts of the package information to be exported. The Options are:

	*Control*	export the package control file as text, suitable for using when building the package outside of PackIt.
	*Copyright*	the text of the copyright tab
	*Sample Command*	a sample Obey file showing how to run the packitcmd command line utility. This Obey file will need modifying before use.

*Help*	Opens the Main help page

*Help On this Tab*	Opens the help at the page describing the current tab.